title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Lotto' game
maintext:
SPRINGFIELD, Ill. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Illinois Lottery’s “Lotto” game were:
04-28-31-37-38-50, Extra Shot: 11
(four, twenty-eight, thirty-one, thirty-seven, thirty-eight, fifty; Extra Shot: eleven)
Estimated jackpot: $8.5 million
